      },
      {
        "step_no": 6,
        "text": "Stir in chili powder, ground cumin, dried oregano, black pepper and salt, coating the meat and vegetables with the spices and cooking one minute to toast the spices.",
        "time_min": 1
      },
      {
        "step_no": 7,
        "text": "Pour in crushed tomatoes and chicken broth, scraping up any fond from the bottom of the pot to incorporate flavor.",
        "time_min": 3
      },
      {
        "step_no": 8,
        "text": "Add drained beans (and optional third bean if using) and bring the mixture to a gentle simmer over medium heat.",
